          "content": {
            "format": "markdown",
            "value": "## Your first program\n\nWhen learning a new language, every programmer's first program prints \"Hello, World!\".\n\nIn Python, we use the `print()` function to output content."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "codeBlock",
          "id": "block-hello-example",
          "position": { "order": 1 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "language": "python",
            "code": "print(\"Hello, World!\")"
          }
        },
        {
